title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - Aircraft & Avionics Update 2 - new build available
description:
In this video we will go through the changes in the third beta build of Aircraft & Avionics Update (AAU) 2 which has been released earlier this week. The third build contains several fixes for issues reported by simmers but in addition to this it again brings new functionality to both Boeings, somethings we saw in the 2nd build also.
